title: 3BD- Dogs Allowed - Upper unit duplex - Avail Sept 1st or sooner
posting_body: ['Hey All my Northeast dwellers!', ':)', 'READ BELOW AND THEN TEXT DREW', 'IF INTERESTED', '*IF INTERESTED PLEASE TEXT ME @ (6-ONE-2) 5SIX8 44THREE5 - Please include your name and a little about yourself so I can best keep track of all the inquiries.*', '3BD - 1BA Unit Available for rent Sept 1st or sooner', '$1595/mo', 'Northeast Minneapolis near ALL the breweries', 'DOG Friendly (HUGE fenced in yard.)', '1 OFF street parking spot', 'Washer and dryer on site', 'Yard to grow a garden', 'Tenant pays for electric and gas average through the year $120/mo', 'Landlords: We are Twin brothers that love our renters.', 'We see it as a relationship rather than business transaction.', 'My brother and I are on the mission to change the landlord stereotype and strive for the best customer care to our renters.', 'We want our renters to take ownership of their property and take care of it as their own.', '*IF INTERESTED PLEASE TEXT ME @ (6-ONE-2) 5SIX8 44THREE5 - Please include your name and a little about yourself so I can best keep track of all the inquiries.*', 'Tenant must do a background check.', "Renter's credentials: tenant's total income 3x the rent, good credit score,  Tenant pays all utilities and snow care", '*IF INTERESTED PLEASE TEXT ME @ (6-ONE-2) 5SIX8 44THREE5 - Please include your name and a little about yourself so I can best keep track of all the inquiries.*']
